o guide enterprise actions.',\n    careers_url: 'https://jobs.medallia.com/',\n    recruiters: [\n      contact(\n        'Chris Pitorri',\n        'Corporate IT Technical Recruiter',\n        'https://www.linkedin.com/in/chrispitorri',\n        'Washington, DC Metro Area, United States',\n        'Corporate IT and technical recruiting',\n        'Public LinkedIn profile identifies Chris as an experienced Corporate IT Technical Recruiter at Medallia.'\n      ),\n      contact(\n        'Yohan Medina',\n        'Senior Recruiter',\n        'https://mx.linkedin.com/in/yohan-medina-a9408b162',\n        'Mexico City, Mexico',\n        'Senior recruiting, client services and regional hiring',\n        'Public LinkedIn profile identifies Yohan as a senior recruiter at Medallia and shows active Medallia hiring posts.'\n      )\n    ]\n  },\n  C0562: {\n    description: 'Pendo delivers product analytics, in-app guidance, feedback, and roadmapping tools that help software teams understand usage and improve digital experiences.',\n    hq_location: 'Raleigh, NC',\n    careers_url: 'https://www.pendo.io/careers/',\n    recruiters: [\n      contact(\n        'Camille Schulz',\n        'Sr. Manager, Recruiting Operations',\n        'https://www.linkedin.com/in/camillebrenkwitz',\n        'Vancouver, WA, United States',\n        'Recruiting operations, talent acquisition systems, SaaS hiring',\n        'Public LinkedIn, The Org, Gem, and BrightHire sources identify Camille as a recruiting operations leader at Pendo.io.'\n      ),\n      contact(\n        'Tamar David',\n        'Talent Acquisition Partner & Recruiting Project Manager',\n        '',\n        'Israel',\n        'Mobile SDK, Android, iOS, and technical support hiring',\n        'Public LinkedIn job posts for Pendo list Tamar as the direct poster for Android, iOS, and technical support roles.'\n      )\n    ]\n  },\n  C0563: {\n    description: 'Gainsight builds customer success and product experience software, including AI-powered retention and adoption tools for SaaS teams managing customer journeys.',\n    careers_url: 'https://www.gainsight.com/careers/',\n    recruiters: [\n      contact(\n        'Meghan Harris Arvidson',\n        'Senior Talent Acquisition Partner',\n        'https://www.linkedin.com/in/meghanharvidson',\n        'South Hamilton, MA, United States',\n        'US talent acquisition, corporate and technical-adjacent roles',\n        'Public LinkedIn profile and Gainsight job posts identify Meghan as Senior Talent Acquisition Partner at Gainsight.'\n      ),\n      contact(\n        'Ramya K.',\n        'Senior Talent Acquisition Partner',\n        'https://in.linkedin.com/in/ramya-k-b6662b161',\n        'Hyderabad, Telangana, India',\n        'Technical recruiting, engineering roles, global and campus hiring',\n        'Public LinkedIn profile and Gainsight engineering job posts identify Ramya as Senior Talent Acquisition Partner at Gainsight.'\n      )\n    ]\n  },\n  C0566: {\n    description: 'Coupa provides cloud spend management software for procurement, supply chain, sourcing, invoicing, expenses, and financial planning across enterprise operations.',\n    hq_location: 'San Mateo, CA',\n    careers_url: 'https://careers.coupa.com/',\n    recruiters: [\n      contact(\n        'Timothy Cushing',\n        'Sr. Technical Recruiter III',\n        'https://www.linkedin.com/in/timothy-cushing-70067863',\n        'San Mateo, CA, United States',\n        'Technical recruiting and engineering talent acquisition',\n        'Public Growjo/LinkedIn snippets identify Timothy as Sr Technical Recruiter III at Coupa Software.'\n      ),\n      contact(\n        'Chris Bartolo',\n        'VP, Talent Acquisition',\n        'https://www.linkedin.com/in/chris-bartolo-77673',\n        'United States',\n        'Global talent acquisition leadership and recruiting process',\n        'Coupa careers page lists Chris as VP Talent Acquisition; public LinkedIn activity discusses Coupa hiring and TA practices.'\n      )\n    ]\n  },\n  C0567: {\n    description: 'Anaplan offers AI-infused scenario planning and analysis software that helps finance, supply chain, sales, and workforce teams model business decisions.',\n    careers_url: 'https://www.anaplan.com/careers/',\n    recruiters: [\n      contact(\n        'Katie Creegan',\n        'Technical Recruiter',\n        'https://www.linkedin.com/in/kacreegan',\n        'Boston, MA, United States',\n        'Technical recruiting, product and platform-adjacent hiring',\n        'Public LinkedIn profile identifies Katie at Anaplan with technical recruiting background and active Anaplan hiring posts.'\n      ),\n      contact(\n        'Andrew Bingham',\n        'Recruiter',\n        'https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrewkbingham',\n        'Miami-Fort Lauderdale Area, United States',\n        'SaaS recruiting, presales and GTM hiring',\n        'Public LinkedIn profile lists Andrew at Anaplan in South Florida; recommendations reference his recruiter outreach for Anaplan roles.'\n      )\n    ]\n  }\n};\n\nfor (const [id, patch] of Object.entries(updates)) {\n  const company = data.companies.find(c => c.id === id);\n  if (\"'!company) throw new Error(`Missing company ${id}`);\n  if ((company.recruiters || []).length) throw new Error(`${id} already has recruiters`);\n  Object.assign(company, patch);\n}\n\nfs.writeFileSync(path, JSON.stringify(data, null, 2) + '\"'\\\\n');\nNODE\"","aggregated_output":"","exit_code":null,"status":"in_progress"}}
