ter / Talent Acquisition Professional',\n        linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jenniferparkerrecruit',\n        email: '',\n        location: 'United States',\n        focus_area: 'Product recruiting, talent acquisition, SaaS hiring',\n        connected: false,\n        messaged: false,\n        responded: false,\n        date_contacted: '',\n        notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile lists Conga and recruiting/talent acquisition experience, including product recruiting recommendation.'\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  C0584: {\n    description: 'Appian provides an AI process automation platform that helps enterprises build applications, orchestrate workflows, automate decisions, and modernize operations.',\n    hq_location: 'McLean, VA',\n    careers_url: 'https://appian.com/careers',\n    linkedin_url_verified: true,\n    recruiters: [\n      {\n        name: 'Mary Kate Messina (Olson)',\n        title: 'Early Career Talent Acquisition Leader',\n        linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/mary-kate-messina-olson-0a466796',\n        email: '',\n        location: 'Charlottesville, VA, United States',\n        focus_area: 'University recruiting, early career, internships, new graduate hiring',\n        connected: false,\n        messaged: false,\n        responded: false,\n        date_contacted: '',\n        notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile lists Appian and early-career university talent acquisition focus.'\n      },\n      {\n        name: 'Jordan Tonelson',\n        title: 'Corporate Recruiter / Talent Acquisition',\n        linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jordan-tonelson-16a37a10a',\n        email: '',\n        location: 'Washington, DC, United States',\n        focus_area: 'Corporate recruiting, technical and customer success hiring',\n        connected: false,\n        messaged: false,\n        responded: false,\n        date_contacted: '',\n        notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile lists Appian and corporate recruiting background; activity ref