erified\\\\\\\": false,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"recruiter_search_url\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/people/?keywords=Company%20Name%20recruiter\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"careers_url\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"recruiters\\\\\\\": []\\\\n}\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nAfter the batch, run the status command again and print this exact marker on its own line:\\\\n\\\\n`=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE edhr <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===`\\\\n\\\",\\\"exit_code\\\":0,\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\"}}\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/media-batch-0005-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE media <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/consulting-batch-0006-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE consulting <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/fintech-batch-0009-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE fintech <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/health-batch-0007-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE health <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/logistics-batch-0002-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE logistics <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/insurance-batch-0007-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE insurance <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/defense-batch-0008-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE defense <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/fintech-batch-0004-prompt.tx